{"tid":1276132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推爆呢個post］唔好再自殺唔好再跳！","createTime":"2019-07-02T01:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:53:04.000Z","uid":91605,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbd82da2d3d3b1e0123444c7c224c5447c7ef3f","tid":1276132,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:36:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你可能覺得好絕望，好無力，堅持無意思，希望以死令大家留意呢件事，但</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解？！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個仆街政府唔會在意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兩個星期林鄭有冇為一個死都出嚟講過嘢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冇，一次都冇。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宜家有人衝擊，撞玻璃，佢地先出嚟屌人衝擊咋。</span>[/size=6]</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再以死明志，呢個仆街政府，仆街林鄭係唔會在意。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要一齊頂住行到最尾！！！</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>多你一個真係好多！！！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線（24小時 ）：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會（廣東話 ）：2389 2222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會（多語言） ：2896 0000<br />\n生命熱線（廣東話）： 2382 0000<br />\n協青社青少年服務（廣東話）：9088 1023<br />\n明愛向晴軒（廣東話）： 18288"},{"pid":"aee60397ddf93d7fd191a68cd5fc35a2a7074f98","tid":1276132,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:37:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e919a192347727baa50a150c3402c301a88e4e1","tid":1276132,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit